## Hints & warnings
This commit includes the PR #7488 rename plus deprecated compatibility wrappers for old Turn/SubAgent factory method names. The old methods intentionally warn with DeprecationWarning and delegate to the new start_* methods. Keep the aliases until the project decides to remove the deprecated method surface.

## Codebase discoveries
Conversation SDK deprecation compatibility already exists for the Session to Conversation rename in weave/conversation/_deprecated.py and tests/conversation/test_deprecation.py. The new compatibility wrappers live in the main conversation module because they are instance methods on Turn/SubAgent, not top-level legacy session aliases.

